{"tid":2046124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國黑警壓頸就暴動 香港南亞男疑遭警壓頸就冇人理","createTime":"2020-06-01T08:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T12:24:58.000Z","uid":13745,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"0feaab910adc108b39661547fe7699f48b7319fa","tid":2046124,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:09:22.000Z","msg":"【致命武力】南亞男疑遭警壓頸亡 巴裔港人警總抗議<br />\n<br />\n本月初涉嫌在尖沙嘴街頭刑毀車輛的南亞男子，因逮捕時反抗遭警員及途人按壓頭頸及手腳合力制服，但他送院一日後死亡。多名目擊者質疑當時警員以膝頭壓着疑犯頸部要害超過兩分鐘，即使事主呼喊「好痛」、「唔好抝（手）」亦未理會，做法有問題。去年水炮車染藍清真寺事件中，曾以流利廣東話批評香港警察的巴基斯坦裔商人簡浩名，今日中午在多名區議員及人權組織成員陪同下，到灣仔警察總部抗議警方使用過份武力，向警務處處長鄧炳強遞交請願信，要求警方正視警暴問題。簡浩名稱：「今日死嘅係一個南亞人，咁聽日呢，會唔會下一個係香港人呢？」"},{"pid":"ed84981f46cc8d1588e6f30caecd0bc4e1c2685e","tid":2046124,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c88ac6aa7fcbe777fff1066246a01d80dbb5a74","tid":2046124,"uid":13745,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:13:02.000Z","msg":"香港南亞人到而家都唔暴動 乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae235fed1355d7bc731c33de8e9221858f17989","tid":2046124,"uid":217232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:13:38.000Z","msg":"其實佢真係死得不明不白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d26cbff3417c8d622f4e82cbb10e6162daa1b75","tid":2046124,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0feaab910adc108b39661547fe7699f48b7319fa","tid":2046124,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited